section.section:
The results shall be reported within 3 months after the close of the fiscal year for the county board on the form and in the manner required by the State Board to:
The State Superintendent;
The county fiscal authority;
The Joint Audit Committee of the General Assembly;
The Senate Budget and Taxation Committee;
The Senate Education, Health, and Environmental Affairs Committee;
The House Appropriations Committee; and
The House Committee on Ways and Means.
